title: Quarterback Combine Preview
itunes:title: Quarterback Combine Preview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode. To start off, DJ gives the average combine numbers of some of the top quarterbacks in the league (3:38). After, the guys preview the quarterbacks that will be at the combine and discuss what they’re looking forward to seeing from them (8:28).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
